body_html:
@yf225

I found out the reason in the log. It says:

-- Could NOT find OpenMP_C (missing: OpenMP_C_FLAGS OpenMP_C_LIB_NAMES)
-- Found OpenMP_CXX: -Xclang -fopenmp

So it'll be fine after we set OpenMP_C_FLAGS.

Actually we are changing compilers between builds. So it seems that we should clean before building again.
